 server have a higher need for mages then necros, that probably stems from low mage numbers rather then needing over 5 mages to help the raid force. why would a guild looking only for more dps/faster kills want a mage over a wizard?  they wouldn't.<br /><br />finally, in regards to soloing.. would you give up your ability to solo w/o a fight? would you say, "hey, soloing was never really intended anyway, so that is ok, all is well now."  if you can honestly say that, then i will let you get by posting your thoughts on why mages have no reason to be upset.</span id="msg"></font></td>
