 kit plz?)<br /><br />That is just a few.  It's sick.  It's really sick because this shit didn't start until that patch that changed Reclaim Energy.  Mages are just on a fucking temper tantrum because they "Want something in return."  Then add to the equation that only 33% of them solo, 33% of them raid, adn the other 33% of them just group.  The leftover 1% are just retards.<br /><br /><blockquote id="quote"><font size="1" face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" id="quote">quote:<hr height="1" noshade id="quote">again, no.. in my experiences watching a bst's pet, and looking at various parses from fights, what i have notice in regards to the bst pet is that it puts out significantly less dmg than mage/necro pets, but it seems to have quite a few more hps..<hr height="1" noshade id="quote"></font id="quote"></blockquote id="quote"><br />Dummy who the hell do you think you're talking to.  I have some fucking logs that show how a BST pet completely owns mine in terms of damage output.  Necro pets sux, that is no fucking mystery.  Mages will just tell you it's because we don't rely on our pets.  Tell me when I'll be kiting around Mithaniel Marr and then I'll fall for that shit.<br /><br /><blockquote id="quote"><font size="1" face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" id="quote">quote:<hr height="1" noshade id="quote">the arguement about mage summoned items and mage ds's is only semi valid, as the necro pet can also be given these same things..<hr height="1" noshade id="quote"></font id="quote"></blockquote id="quote"><br />Then the mage who gave them to the Necro pet or is whoring his ass in Bazaar selling them is just fucking himself.  Thank you very much for making my pet equivalent to yours see you later here is your 20pp.  Yes it's viable because BST and NEC cannot summon this shit.  If there is no mage in your group you are on a search for this shit.  Mage has no problem creating a 5k HP pet with 11% more haste, as if they needed more to begin with.  Also take into effect that their pets hav